'''乔尔·侯布匈'''（{{lang-fr|'''Joël Robuchon'''}}，{{IPA-fr|ʒɔɛl ʁobyʃɔ̃}}，{{bd|1945年|4月7日|2018年|8月6日|catIdx=Robuchon}}），法國廚師、「[[赫布匈美食坊|L'Atelier de Joël Robuchon]]」餐廳創辦人。[[戈和米約|戈和米約]]美食指南曾於1989年稱他為「世紀主廚」（Chef of the Century）。<ref>{{Cite news |first=Jennifer |last=Leuzzi |title=A Top Chef Arrives in New York (Finally) |url=http://www.nysun.com/article/37595 |work=The New York Sun |date=2006-08-09 |accessdate=2007-11-25 |language=en |archive-date=2008-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724035928/http://www.nysun.com/article/37595 }}</ref>

== 生平 ==
侯布雄在1945年出生於法國[[普瓦捷|普瓦捷]]，有三個兄弟姊妹，父母分別是砌磚及清潔工人，<ref name=Joël>{{cite news |author1=<!--None--> |title=世纪厨神 Joël Robuchon 离世 曾说“压力太大了，我想好好生活” |url=http://fashion.sina.com.cn/l/ts/rs/2018-08-06/2016/doc-ihhhczfc6816043.shtml |work=[[新浪網|新浪網]] |date=2018-08-06 |accessdate=2019-07-26 |archive-date=2019-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726113323/http://fashion.sina.com.cn/l/ts/rs/2018-08-06/2016/doc-ihhhczfc6816043.shtml }}</ref>一家篤信[[天主教|天主教]]。<ref name=Robuchon>{{cite news |author1=Coco Huang |title=世紀廚神侯布雄走了，這五件事情你不能忘記他 |url=https://www.elle.com/tw/life/g22658748/joelrobuchon-death/ |work=[[ELLE|ELLE]]（香港） |date=2018-08-07 |accessdate=2019-07-26 |archive-date=2021-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211011073435/https://www.elle.com/tw/life/g22658748/joelrobuchon-death/ }}</ref>他年少時曾經在修道院轄下寄宿学校唸書，13歲已立志當一名神父，但之後於協助修女烹煮食物期間，發現自己頗具料理天份，覺得天主對自己另有「召喚」，故此15歲便決定進入第一間餐廳工作，繼而開始向飲食界發展。<ref name=Robuchon/>他亦曾在[[德塞夫勒省|德塞夫勒省]][[莫雷翁|莫雷翁]]瑟福尔神学院任職廚師，36歲時於[[巴黎|巴黎]]開設了第一家餐館，1976年以優秀的廚藝獲得「[[法國最佳工匠獎|法國最佳工匠獎]]」殊榮。<ref name=Joël/>

侯布雄主力推廣法國[[新潮烹調|新潮烹調]]（Nouvelle Cuisine），<ref>{{cite news |author1=万刀甲 |title=【法國廚神 Joël Robuchon 逝世】死前最想吃「壽司之神」？ |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%BD%A2%E8%80%8C/219818/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%BB%9A%E7%A5%9Ejo%C3%ABl-robuchon%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E6%AD%BB%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%80%E6%83%B3%E5%90%83-%E5%A3%BD%E5%8F%B8%E4%B9%8B%E7%A5%9E |work=[[香港01|香港01]] |date=2018-08-07 |accessdate=2019-07-26 |archive-date=2019-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726113327/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%BD%A2%E8%80%8C/219818/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%BB%9A%E7%A5%9Ejo%C3%ABl-robuchon%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E6%AD%BB%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%80%E6%83%B3%E5%90%83-%E5%A3%BD%E5%8F%B8%E4%B9%8B%E7%A5%9E }}</ref>並出版過多本食譜（其中有兩本譯為英文），擔任{{tsl|en|Larousse Gastronomique|拉魯斯美食百科}}委員會主席和主持烹飪節目。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Chefs Around the World |newspaper=Travel International |pages=28 |date=Spring 2005 |url=http://www.stardiamondaward.com/newsletter/objects/TI_Spring05_4.pdf |format=PDF |postscript=<!--None--> |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071128152532/http://www.stardiamondaward.com/newsletter/objects/TI_Spring05_4.pdf |archivedate=2007-11-28 |accessdate=2018-08-06 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wiley.com/WileyCDA/WileyTitle/productCd-0471292974,descCd-authorInfo.html |title=L'Atelier of Joel Robuchon: The Artistry of a Master Chef and His Proteges |accessdate=2007-11-25 |publisher=Wiley & Sons |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071214145440/http://www.wiley.com/WileyCDA/WileyTitle/productCd-0471292974,descCd-authorInfo.html |archive-date=2007-12-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>直至2006年，他創辦了「[[赫布匈美食坊|L'Atelier de Joël Robuchon]]」，在[[亞洲|亞洲]]、[[歐洲|歐洲]]與[[北美洲|北美洲]]擁有十多家店舖，<ref>{{cite news |author1=<!--None--> |title=名厨赫布匈的香港美食坊 |url=https://www.wine-world.com/topic/103313932/20130729165720247 |work=红酒世界网 |date=2013-07-29 |accessdate=2019-07-26 |archive-date=2019-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726113325/https://www.wine-world.com/topic/103313932/20130729165720247 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Rocky Hsu |title=獨家專訪法國世紀名廚 – 侯布雄 Joël Robuchon |url=https://jazko.com/featured/joel-robuchon-interview/ |work=[[Jazko|Jazko]] |date=2017-10-26 |accessdate=2019-07-26 |archive-date=2020-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222230634/http://jazko.com/featured/joel-robuchon-interview/ }}</ref>更曾取得31顆[[米其林指南|米其林指南]]星級（2017年增至35顆，<ref>{{cite news |author1=凃盈如 |title=重現侯布雄星光宴！世紀名廚接班團隊來台獻藝 |url=https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2736898 |work=[[自由時報|自由時報]] |date=2019-03-23 |accessdate=2019-07-26 |archive-date=2019-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726113321/https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2736898 }}</ref>主要來自亞洲分店），為全世界米其林星級總數最多的主廚，<ref name=stars>{{Cite news |author=Ng Kai Ling |last= |title=Local flavour, world-class food |url=http://www.straitstimes.com/BreakingNews/Singapore/Story/STIStory_593266.html |work=The Straits Times |date=2010-10-20 |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108071717/http://www.straitstimes.com/BreakingNews/Singapore/Story/STIStory_593266.html |archive-date=2010-11-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>''Masterchef: The Professionals 2010'' (Episode 16)</ref>又曾教導出不少名廚，其中最有名的弟子是[[戈登·拉姆齊|戈登·拉姆齊]]。

他被確診[[胰腺癌|胰腺癌]]之後，於[[日内瓦|日内瓦]]接受治療，惟2018年8月6日因病逝世，終年73歲。<ref>{{cite news |author1=中央通訊社 |title=侯布雄73歲病逝 擁有最多米其林星星的世紀名廚 |url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201808065003-1.aspx |work=[[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |date=2018-08-07 |accessdate=2018-08-06 |archive-date=2018-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806150311/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201808065003-1.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=<!--None--> |title=【31顆米芝蓮星星】法國名廚盧布松逝世　終年73歲 |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20180806/s00005/1533559228661/%E3%80%9031%E9%A1%86%E7%B1%B3%E8%8A%9D%E8%93%AE%E6%98%9F%E6%98%9F%E3%80%91%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%90%8D%E5%BB%9A%E7%9B%A7%E5%B8%83%E6%9D%BE%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B473%E6%AD%B2 |work=[[明報|明報新聞網]] |date=2018-08-06 |accessdate=2019-07-26 |archive-date=2019-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726113323/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B/article/20180806/s00005/1533559228661/%25E3%2580%259031%25E9%25A1%2586%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E8%258A%259D%25E8%2593%25AE%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%2598%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25BB%259A%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%259D%25BE%25E9%2580%259D%25E4%25B8%2596-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25B9%25B473%25E6%25AD%25B2 }}</ref>

